a.text: First, we must prepare the pasture for the horse!
Let’s leave the toolbox here. You won’t need it.
Place some seats around the place
Would also be nice to add some curtains
Tidying up whatever was left from the pasture
We need to cut the chains to get in
Let’s chop this tree down as well
Almost there! A few more flowers
Next up, we must care for her coat and hooves.
Then we apply some horse care products
This is going to take a while...
Almost there! Just a little elbow grease...
Let’s wash and dry her up!
While the horse rests a bit, let’s construct a dressage arena
First, we must brush her thoroughly
Then furnish her with a saddle
Let’s give her some water to drink
Oh, a hole! Let’s fill it up.
Let’s build another bar for her to jump over
Let’s dry her well afterward so she won’t get cold.
